tool_description:
Calculates the coefficient of how similar are 2 strings containing the name (and type) of the route. With a value of 0.9 and higher, it is possible to do auto-matching,
at 0.2-0.9 - visual matching.
name: Compare Route Names
title: Compare Route Names
